<translation id="1554523534964039554">Yabelana Ngamaphasiwedi Neqembu lakho Lomndeni</translation>
<translation id="1556556838855011466">1. Vula iChrome</translation>
<translation id="2319645462410562206">IChrome ingathola izinombolo zokulandelela ozifaka kumasayithi futhi ibonise izibuyekezo zephakheji Ekhasini Lethebhu Entsha.</translation>
<translation id="2551790923936684824">Landelela le Phakheji?</translation>
